                            我的帐户
                        </h5>
                        <div class="list-group list-group-flush has-icons" style=" display: inline-block; ">
                            <div style="float:left;width: 49%;display: inline-block;">
                                <a href="/Customer/ContributePoints" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action menu-link" style="display:table;">
                                    <div style="text-align:center;">
                                        <img src='@Url.Content("~/Content/Images/icons/design16.png")'  style="margin-right:0px;" alt="" />
                                    @*<i class="fal fa-fw fal fa-lightbulb list-group-item-icon" style="margin-right:0px;"></i>*@
                                    </div>
                                    <div style="text-align:center;"><span>贡献值数量</span></div>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                            <div style="width: 2%; display: inline-block; "><b style="font-size: x-large; color: #a9a9a9; ">|</b></div>
